The MongoDB 2.0.0 Driver docs at: http://mongodb.github.io/node-mongodb-native/2.0/tutorials/gridfs/ states: 

{quote}
{{gs.stream([autoclose=false])}}
where
autoclose If true current GridStore will be closed when EOF and ‘close’ event will be fired
{quote}

However looking at the code I can't see any implementation for {{autoclose}} and checking whether the stream has in fact autoclosed indicates it hasn't.

Further the API Docs don't mention {{autoclose}}.

